#: .\core\presets.py:5
msgid "1-4-2 Lung Conditioning Pattern"
msgstr "Pola Pengkondisian Paru 1-4-2"

#: .\core\presets.py:13
msgid ""
"A classic respiratory conditioning sequence designed to maximize blood "
"oxygenation and expand vital lung capacity over time."
msgstr ""
"Urutan pengkondisian pernapasan klasik yang dirancang untuk memaksimalkan "
"oksigenasi darah dan memperluas kapasitas vital paru seiring waktu."

#: .\core\presets.py:16
msgid "Box Breathing (Navy SEAL Tactical Clarity)"
msgstr "Box Breathing (Kejelasan Taktis Navy SEAL)"

#: .\core\presets.py:24
msgid ""
"The gold standard for high-stress grounding. Equal duration phases clear "
"cortisol, settle racing hearts, and restore sharp mental clarity."
msgstr ""
"Standar utama untuk menenangkan diri dari stres tinggi. Fase berdurasi sama "
"menurunkan kortisol, menstabilkan jantung yang berdebar, dan memulihkan "
"kejelasan mental."

#: .\core\presets.py:27
msgid "4-7-8 Relaxation (Nervous System Tranquilizer)"
msgstr "Relaksasi 4-7-8 (Penenang Sistem Saraf)"

#: .\core\presets.py:35
msgid ""
"Acts as a natural chemical brake for your sympathetic nervous system. Highly "
"recommended for severe anxiety and floating into deep sleep."
msgstr ""
"Bertindak sebagai rem kimia alami untuk sistem saraf simpatik Anda. Sangat "
"direkomendasikan untuk kecemasan parah dan membantu tidur nyenyak."

#: .\core\presets.py:38
msgid "Coherent / Resonant Breathing (Asthma & Panic Relief)"
msgstr "Pernapasan Koheren / Resonan (Meredakan Asma & Panik)"

#: .\core\presets.py:46
msgid ""
"Balances the vagus nerve and optimizes heart rate variability (HRV). Zero "
"hold times make this perfectly safe for active asthma management."
msgstr ""
"Menyeimbangkan saraf vagus dan mengoptimalkan variabilitas detak jantung "
"(HRV). Tanpa waktu jeda menahan napas membuatnya sangat aman untuk "
"pengelolaan asma aktif."

#: .\core\presets.py:49
msgid "Tactical Breathing (Sustained Equilibrium)"
msgstr "Pernapasan Taktis (Keseimbangan Berkelanjutan)"

#: .\core\presets.py:57
msgid ""
"A specialized, low-overhead holding variant used by responders to reduce "
"somatic anxiety without inducing lightheadedness."
msgstr ""
"Varian penahanan napas khusus berbeban rendah yang digunakan oleh petugas "
"darurat untuk mengurangi kecemasan somatik tanpa memicu pusing."

#: .\core\presets.py:60
msgid "Pursed-Lip Splinting (COPD & Air-Trapping Relief)"
msgstr "Pursed-Lip Splinting (Meredakan PPOK & Penjebakan Udara)"

#: .\core\presets.py:68
msgid ""
"Creates passive mechanical backpressure to keep bronchial pathways open. "
"Crucial for individuals with emphysema or structural shortness of breath."
msgstr ""
"Menciptakan tekanan balik mekanis pasif untuk menjaga saluran bronkial tetap "
"terbuka. Sangat penting bagi individu dengan emfisema atau sesak napas "
"struktural."

#: .\core\presets.py:71
msgid "Physiological Sigh (Acute Hyperventilation Intercept)"
msgstr "Physiological Sigh (Mengatasi Hiperventilasi Akut)"

#: .\core\presets.py:79
msgid ""
"Simulates the biological double-inhale reflex to instantly re-inflate "
"collapsed alveoli and maximize immediate carbon dioxide unloading."
msgstr ""
"Meniru refleks biologis menarik napas ganda untuk langsung mengembangkan "
"kembali alveoli yang mengempis dan memaksimalkan pelepasan karbon dioksida "
"secara instan."

#: .\core\presets.py:82
msgid "Extended Cardiac Exhale (Hypertension / Vagal Tone)"
msgstr "Pernapasan Buang Napas Diperpanjang (Kontrol Hipertensi / Tonus Vagal)"

#: .\core\presets.py:90
msgid ""
"Exhale window is mathematically doubled relative to inhale. Maximizes "
"acetylcholinergic outflow to safely downregulate heart rate and blood "
"pressure."
msgstr ""
"Waktu menghembuskan napas secara matematis digandakan relatif terhadap "
"menarik napas. Memaksimalkan aliran asetilkolinergik untuk menurunkan detak "
"jantung dan tekanan darah dengan aman."

